WEBVTT

00:02.551 --> 00:04.791
A duckling hatched in the barnyard.

00:05.630 --> 00:09.281
It was too grey, too large and too clumsy.

00:10.345 --> 00:13.611
The other animals mistreated him, so he left.

00:16.161 --> 00:20.688
Almost a year later, he saw some beautiful swans in a pond.

00:21.707 --> 00:23.405
He was afraid to approach them.

00:24.241 --> 00:28.032
But to his surprise, they welcomed and accepted him.

00:29.001 --> 00:30.451
He gazed at his reflection...

00:30.965 --> 00:34.783
...and saw that he too was a beautiful swan.

